{
  "stem": "10905.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And you could see the-- the sugar trail coming out of the-- whenever I see one of those films in the movie theaters, I always think back of my youth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It took us a fairly arduous trip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I really don't recall it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We had to cross rivers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we had to-- my mother buried her jewelry someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We took a raft across.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Finally, we got to the part of Yugoslavia that had been returned to Hungary, where my mother's family was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And we stayed in Subotica, which now had become Szabadka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Now, my language at that time was Serbian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And, of course, my mother spoke perfect Hungarian because she was from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "My dad wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "The rest of the family had lived in [INAUDIBLE], spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So I was-- [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- he was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the war was on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germany had invaded Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yugoslavia had decided they were going to resist Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was an officer in the Army, and he was not with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Jews were not thought as anything different than anybody else in Yugoslavia at that time-- the Yugoslavs, the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Croats-- that's a different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Serbs never thought of the Jews as being the enemy, or they were never, ever very partisan towards the Germans or their way of thinking.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived to members of my mother's family, and finally we worked our way back to Subotica.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was not allowed to go out of the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed with some relatives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was allowed to go in the courtyard, which was an enclosed courtyard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on like a farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
